      "para_id": "Q001374.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Enlil , the king of all lands , his master , Lugal-kisale-si , king of Unug , king of Urim , firstborn child of Lugal-kiĝeneš-dudu , king of Unug , king of Urim , dedicated this ( vessel ) for his well-being ."
    }
